snippet.textDisplay:
Oh boy, I have a dentist story...

I had to get a root canal and I was terrified. I was 16 or 17...old enough to be super into girls and of course two absolutely beautiful nurses were there to help me.

I thought they were going to put me to sleep but I too got the "we don't do that here" and I began to freak out... I was shaking but trying to hide it so these two hot girls don't think I'm a loser.

The dentist numbed me and started working. My fear burst out into crying but then I realized I wasn't in pain but I was still scared so I started laughing at myself... So there I was... Two beautiful nurses watching me hysterically laugh with tears running down my face and the look for absolute fear and embarrassment overwhelming me.

I never went back there.
